## ğŸ›  How to Run Locally

1. Clone this repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/63rude/Stat-Hackathon-Website
   cd Stat-Hackathon-Website

2. Make sure your Python FastAPI backend is running locally (e.g., at http://localhost:8000)

3. Install dependencies and start the frontend dev server:
    pnpm install
    pnpm run dev

4. Open the URL printed in the terminal (usually http://localhost:5173) to use the chatbot interface.